title: The Edmonton Oilers Cup Run of 2006 - SCF vs The Canes
description:
Are you able to watch Game 7? I haven&#039;t seen it yet and never will. But it&#039;s included here for your viewing displeasure.

What could have been. If only Berge**** hadn&#039;t pushed the guy into Roli, if only Conklin hadn&#039;t been a complete clown, if only...

Still, there are some great moments here, and none better than Pisani&#039;s shortie. Enjoy, and pick the games you want.
